    public static class BleNodeConfig.DefaultTaskTimeoutRequestFilter

implements BleNodeConfig.TaskTimeoutRequestFilter
    Default implementation of BleNodeConfig.TaskTimeoutRequestFilter that simply sets the timeout for all BleTask instances to DEFAULT_TASK_TIMEOUT seconds.
